Then write the list to a group

list_to_h5group.Rd

This function writes a list to an H5Group, creating datasets for each element. If the list contains nested lists, it will create subgroups.

Usage

list_to_h5group(h5fg, name, lst)

Arguments

h5fg

An H5File or H5Group object where the group will be created

name

The name of the group to create

lst

The list to write to the group

Value

The created H5Group object
